title: URF queue not showing up
body: I can't find the URF queue. Is it not up yet or something?

replies.body: URF is now live for North America. It was only previously available on Oceania and Europe West/Nordic East.

close game and run a repair, that fixed it for me.

Note: I think what caused it is that league was open when the change took place (I leave it open when i sleep/go to work, sometimes i get disconnected but i didn't this time, and when i tried to queue for something the game crashed).
same. Patched, logged in, saw no urf, verified the site says "URF is now live", relogged, still no urf.
The same is happening to me.  Got up all excited to play it and it is nowhere to be found.  If it's disabled, Riot, please let me know before I go crazy.
